item.title: Hilarie Burton Morgan: Grimoire Girl & True Crime Story: It Couldn't Happen Here
item.description: On this episode, Stassi chats with author, podcaster, actress Hilarie Burton Morgan about her latest New York Times Bestselling book Grimoire Girl and her TV show/companion podcast, True Crime Story: It Couldn't Happen Here. Stassi and Hilarie's interests overlap through this entire podcast - from loving New Orleans and Paris, to creating you own oracle deck and writing your own eulogy...
